        "html": "<p><em>EDITOR’S NOTE: This Daily Poster report is being co-published with </em>Newsweek<em>. Please share <a href=\"https://www.newsweek.com/joe-biden-could-stop-post-pandemic-foreclosure-crisis-repeat-obamas-big-mistake-1598594\">this link</a> with others.</em></p>"
